h:100%"><p><span>Is TrueFit a good meal replacement?</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="3fe9c2cb-170a-48d4-9ec3-c824d915ca04" class="r-1w6avjg"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1dqor84" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1fj2:"><div data-rid="05884dcb-73fc-4a58-81fe-3a3982ebe5bb" class="r-kpavxn"><div data-rid="21faada1-338e-4d0c-92dd-1e6142521dc7" class="r-f89k48 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes — it contains protein, fiber, probiotics, and whole-food nutrients to create a balanced, satisfying meal in seconds.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b48becb5-84e7-4d98-8956-42e09147b905" class="r-qn8vo9" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="c8cf4fa2-04ac-4815-a5d5-f015d3c588b2" aria-controls="replo-:R1vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-z57fwu"><div data-rid="d2f5552b-ece9-4d3c-ba10-84f66395e07b" class="r-4pnrr8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Should I use TrueFit if I'm on GLP-1 medications?</p></span></div><div data-rid="1d989143-bf7f-4c5a-892b-bfc8924dc340" class="r-av09gc"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1hupztl" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1vj2:"><div data-rid="24fda29f-e169-4198-a364-ef49c225cab0" class="r-7ea9ym"><div data-rid="5918af85-1066-4223-8a1b-23382a76f887" class="r-112q1do alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Absolutely. GLP-1 medications suppress appetite — TrueFit complements that effect by giving you a nutrient-dense, high-protein shake that keeps you satisfied for hours. Perfect for days when you don’t feel hungry enough for a full meal but still need quality nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3257e949-d00b-4b84-88da-62a266555f37" class="r-1mf9158" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="55987c63-3b96-41f4-8824-6427bbc5c711" aria-controls="replo-:R2fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1k2wpa1"><div data-rid="fcaa5b6f-7749-4e0e-a9fd-222a2c076e8e" class="r-10r9yiq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>Can I use TrueFit even if I'm not on GLP-1 medications?</h3></span></div><div data-rid="710a120f-6803-45ee-9993-dc0273217359" class="r-dvsqyt"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-18b2q3f" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2fj2:"><div data-rid="8041cc4e-99df-4339-b0de-f9c2fceb19f5" class="r-1sbt9v6"><div data-rid="e93a89f2-d6b6-49dd-94e0-d2cb2d3465a5" class="r-gjq9qj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Absolutely. TrueFit works as a natural appetite-supporting, muscle-preserving, clean protein shake for anyone trying to lose weight or improve nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3e1e9615-5915-4aad-8beb-5fa80e8e2fe3" class="r-11lzccw" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="5f10568f-722f-4f8d-8212-ddd0169aef0f" aria-controls="replo-:R2vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1a267ho"><div data-rid="6628ff74-5393-45e5-bcfd-2b4f30fab903" class="r-gavvlg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When should I take TrueFit?</p></span></div><div data-rid="80926313-848f-4560-9c40-295b055986ce" class="r-3kjrt1"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1hwluxo" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2vj2:"><div data-rid="4c1e5ace-5393-4b43-adf8-3d52ada294b0" class="r-tx5kz6"><div data-rid="9919478c-3739-427a-b8c3-0744e8befa7c" class="r-1ehiyxw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>TrueFit is designed to fit seamlessly into any weight-loss routine — with or without GLP-1 medications. You can take it any time you need a filling, nutrient-dense option, but most customers prefer it:</p><p><br>Morning: as a balanced, high-protein breakfast that sets the tone for the day<br><br>Midday: as an easy, satisfying lunch replacement<br><br>Post-Workout: to support lean muscle and recovery<br><br>On low-appetite days: when GLP-1 medications make full meals difficult<br><br>Evenings: as a clean, sweet-tooth-satisfying shake without derailing goals</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6f743bec-7e3d-4813-94a9-faa2d9b117b8" class="r-1ox65on" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="e0a0f0f0-8efa-4d9a-9d80-6bdd8c1d9390" aria-controls="replo-:R3fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1gx171n"><div data-rid="347cd77c-5051-4c20-9fe1-f3bde89995fb" class="r-9f6kxw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span>Will TrueFit help preserve muscle while losing weight?</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="84ea52ea-d136-4174-b6c6-2e0b0331eee8" class="r-1wc7gbn"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" a